{"type": "article", "id": 44606, "title": "Netflix 开大麻快闪店，一个在线“小朋友画廊”很流行 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2017-08-29T05:22:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 2219, "name": "刘诗诗"}, {"id": 171, "name": "Netflix"}, {"id": 1437, "name": "腾讯"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 32, "image": "img/article/article_show/201708291228071Oz0bnjXuyfglBTK.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939; -webkit-text-stroke: #393939} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2017/08/28/tods-names-liushishi-as-its-new-brand-ambassador/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>刘诗诗出任 Tod's 全新品牌大使，还拍了支《寻爱卡普里》的微电影广告</b></a>。Tod's 没有公开其品牌大使履行义务的区域，但从代言规格上来说，品牌大使相较于品牌代言人的职责相对轻松。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=v0543gnklca&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">值得一提的广告</h3><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 15.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; color: #999999; -webkit-text-stroke: #999999} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 15.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; color: #999999; -webkit-text-stroke: #999999; min-height: 20.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939; -webkit-text-stroke: #393939} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939; -webkit-text-stroke: #393939; min-height: 19.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'Songti SC'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #393939; min-height: 25.0px} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'Songti SC'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #393939} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 15.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; font-kerning: none; color: #999999; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #999999} span.s3 {font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-kerning: none; color: #393939; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #393939} </style>  </p><p><b><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2017/08/25/mercedes-amg-releases-its-new-ad-film/\" rel=\"nofollow\">奔驰新广告，拍的是霸王龙复活的乌龙事件。</a></b>以梅赛德斯-AMG（Mercedes-AMG）43 的排气声浪拍摄的悬念广告。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=n0541b847b8&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2017/08/25/laperla-releasesits-2017-fallwinter-film/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>La Perla 公布了 2017 年最新秋冬广告大片。</b></a>金小妹肯达尔·詹娜出镜， 全球知名摄影师双人组 Mert Alas＆Marcus Piggott 担当摄影。Mert&amp;Marcus 是全球最擅长拍摄女性写真的知名摄影师组合，与诸多奢侈品牌如香奈儿、迪奥、路易威登等合作过。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe src=\"http://player.youku.com/embed/XMjk4OTgxODA2OA==\" frameborder=\"0\" 'allowfullscreen'=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/2017/8/netflix-weed-strains-disjointed\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Netflix 新喜剧 Disjointed 讲述大麻药店销售员的故事</b></a>，他们在每一集插播一个虚构品牌的搞笑广告，而且还推出了实体的大麻产品，在好莱坞开快闪店销售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe src=\"https://giphy.com/embed/8SURElmLaeeis\" frameborder=\"0\" class=\"giphy-embed\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe><p><a href=\"https://giphy.com/gifs/adweek-8SURElmLaeeis\" rel=\"nofollow\">via GIPHY</a></p>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170829124710aiAzY4Fs5hUIdvlW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.592593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.digitaling.com/projects/22808.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>麦肯 Humancare 为统一阿萨姆奶茶推出新包装</b></a>，希望改变瓶装奶茶老气的产品定位。还找郭采洁拍了一支方言版歌舞剧“方言大话好心情”<b>。</b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708291251202BV6PY4RyXzQwsuo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.720710\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.sohu.com/a/168045963_114778\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>腾讯公益活动刷屏朋友圈，一元钱逛“小朋友”画廊</b></a>。<a href=\"http://ssl.gongyi.qq.com/m/wxact/gallery.html?from=share&amp;ADTAG=m_share&amp;et=m_share\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里</a>查看 36 幅小朋友的画作。该项目“用艺术点亮生命”由上海艺途公益基金会（WABC）在腾讯公益平台上发起、由具有公募资质的深圳市爱佑未来慈善基金会负责善款接受。捐赠的善款将直接存入接受善款的公募机构账户，可以通过腾讯公益平台直接查询善款的后续使用情况。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170829142404GrFMhLIPpTy9EeVs.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.593750\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 15.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; color: #999999; -webkit-text-stroke: #999999} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: #323333} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 45.0px; font: 15.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; color: #999999; -webkit-text-stroke: #999999} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939; -webkit-text-stroke: #393939} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939; -webkit-text-stroke: #393939; min-height: 19.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 16.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; font-kerning: none; color: #323333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #323333} span.s3 {font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-kerning: none; color: #393939; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #393939} </style>  </p><h3>公司有啥大事发生</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.adquan.com/post-2-41964.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>微信首家品牌形象店 WeStore 正式开业。</b></a>位于微信总部，即 T.I.T 创意园区。WeStore 授权生活文化品牌哲品运营。店内包括周边商店、咖啡厅，以及展示厅。目前该店仅对腾讯员工及访客开放。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170829125943TcPRfqaI5Dzvx8Ys.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.548780\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170829130001LI2ATZe46CvfzSya.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170829130012NftY36qBJLGEnhm2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>最后，也挺重要</h3><p><b><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2017/08/18/groupm-rolls-out-viewability-standards/\" rel=\"nofollow\">WPP 旗下媒体投资管理集团群邑 (GroupM) 今天宣布在全球范围内推出广告可见度标准。</a></b></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170829130314EAMoyxb9WRm7wqfg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707937\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">推动广告行业透明度是近期行业最火的话题之一。群邑的核心客户包括联合利华、金宝汤 、壳牌、赛百味和沃尔沃汽车等都对群邑呼吁和实施数字广告领域更高广告可见度衡量标准的举措表示支持。其中，自 2014 年群邑于美国首度推出广告可见度标准时，联合利华便与群邑展开了合作。</p><p class=\"\">题图来源：<a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/2017/8/netflix-weed-strains-disjointed\" rel=\"nofollow\">hypebeast</a></p>"}